So we have a lot of open questions in our feedback forum because this is something where we really want to focus on to integrate community feedback into our analysis. But it's really hard to go through hundreds of open text feedback in like 30 languages. So we get feedback from France, from Japan, from Brazil, from Russia, and it's like this is not working out without AI. So we are using an LLM to first translate the open text answers and then as well to summarize them. So we actually know what they wrote in the survey.

